title: Re: Jessica Valenti throws creepy temper tantrum over Ivana Trump working to STOP human trafficking
text:
‘Wash her father’s stink off’: Jessica Valenti gets creepy over Ivanka working to stop human trafficking Posted at 12:10 pm on February 23, 2017 by Sam J. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
It would seem Jessica Valenti is upset that Ivanka Trump is working with her father’s administration to focus on halting human trafficking. Any excuse to attack Ivanka … feminism is awful. 
Not entirely sure why anyone would take issue with Ivanka over this , even if you don’t like Donald Trump. We're told that the sudden West Wing attention to human trafficking was driven by @IvankaTrump https://t.co/jRzfum584D 
— Mike Allen (@mikeallen) February 23, 2017 
Then again, we are dealing with feminism: Right on time, as Trump takes away protections for trans kids… https://t.co/qnS87dcMdF 
— Jessica Valenti (@JessicaValenti) February 23, 2017 Trending
